<section class="description">
    <div class="description-text">
        <h1>MineAwareVR</h1>
        <p>MineAware VR is the pre-eminent landmine and explosive remnants of war (ERW) sensitization training for all those who wish to understand the landmine and ERW threat in currently illegally invaded countries as well as how to keep themselves, their colleagues and loved ones safe, if the find themselves in a suspected landmine or ERW contaminated area.</p>
        <p>Safer Access Consulting presents: MineAware VR for the Quest 2 VR platform. MineAware VR has been designed based on hundreds of hours of landmine and explosive remenants of war (ERW) orientation and sensitization training in contexts such as Ukraine.</p>
        <p>MineAware VR provides an interactive theoretical and practical experience for users who are living or working in countries with a real landmine and ERW threat. Knowledge gain from this experience will give the users a realistic exposure to what actual landmines and ERWs look like in the real world, but of course in a controled and safe environment.</p>
        <p>The theory is transformed into practical and real-world applicable skills when users are taught a protocol which will help themselves, their colleagues and loved ones safe, if they find themselves in a suspected landmine or ERW contaminated area.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="description-media">
        <!-- Drop the gameplay screenshot here: wwwroot/images/mineavrevr-gameplay.png -->
